inish, desktop and keyboard tray color are all customizable. No matter what=
 your setup, single or dual monitor, the E7 can be adapted to hold up to tw=
o screens on its VESA mount. Get to your sitting and standing heights in se=
conds with the press of a button thanks to a built-in keypad. Not all conve=
rters are created equal (clearly).</p><h6 class=3D"font-base font-karla tex=
